parts.text: This is an invoice from Clipboard Papers to ACME Systems Inc. for concierge services.  The invoice number is 640419 and the date is June 18, 2017.  One unit of concierge services was provided at a cost of 187,124 RON.  Including tax (37,424.8 RON), the total amount due is 224,549 RON.  Payment is due within seven days of receipt.
